    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>bread roll[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Remove the tray with the wedges from the oven and add the <strong>halved bread roll[s]</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 4-5 min or until toasted and charred</p><p>Once toasted, remove the <strong>halved bread roll[s]</strong> from the oven and rub with the <strong>crushed garlic</strong> - this is your <strong>garlic bread roll</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
