    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>To build your burger, spread a dollop of <strong>balsamic mayo </strong>on the <strong>garlic ciabatta base</strong> and top with a handful of <strong>salad</strong>, a <strong>pork & beef patty</strong>, a spoonful of the <strong>bruschetta mixture</strong> and <strong>garlic ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>bruschetta burger</strong></p>",
