      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>bruschetta burger </strong>with the <strong>oregano wedges </strong>and <strong>remaining salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the salad with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>bruschetta mixture</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
